  "_meta": {
    "title": "Complaint Quality → Planet (action) + State (the WHAT axis)",
    "lineage": "Medical-astrology tradition — the planetary 'pathological action' (Hill's Code: the planet is the WHAT). Distilled, attributed to the tradition, never ingested verbatim.",
    "sources": ["Medical-astrology tradition (planetary pathological action)"],
    "axis": "PLANET = the pathological ACTION; STATE = the engine's imbalance axis (excess/deficiency/blocked). The complaint's QUALITY word decides which — note the Saturn-in-Pisces lesson: the same planet can read excess OR deficiency by quality, so the word, not the planet, sets the state.",
    "note": "Resolver matches a quality word against `match` substrings; all matches feed the polarity engine, which ranks by weight (most-specific/strongest wins as primary). Disambiguation is by SPECIFIC keyword: 'swollen + warm/red' → Mars; 'puffy + soft/heavy' → Jupiter. 'electric/sudden/jolt' → Uranus (not Mercury). Order = most-specific first."
